fields.description:
Affects: 
Page 88 of FlexNet Manager for Engineering Applications 2016 R2 Installation Guide PDF.

Step 5 of 'Post-Installation Configuration Steps' says "Under Reporting, under Report Designer, click Cognos Administration."

However,  Cognos Administration is not shown until the user assigns the admin user to the Cognos roles by going to 'Reporting' -> 'Assign Cognos Roles'. A step describing assigning cognos roles is required.
fields.summary: Post-install instructions for Report Designer missing key step
